OL,3,CLong-lost friends brought back
OL,4,Ctogether by life-saving kidney donation
OL,6,FTwo friends who had drifted apart say
OL,7,Fthey have been brought back together
OL,8,Fby a life-saving kidney donation.
OL,10,FBev Farnsworth from has suffered for
OL,11,Fdecades with polycystic kidney disease
OL,12,F- a genetic disorder which had already
OL,13,Ftaken the life of her mum and
OL,14,Fgrandmother.
OL,16,FShe had already had one kidney removed
OL,17,Fduring cancer treatment and her
OL,18,Fremaining kidney continued to degrade.
