OL,3,CLong-lost friends brought back
OL,4,Ctogether by life-saving kidney donation
OL,6,FDesperate to avoid dialysis, Bev
OL,7,Fturned to social media, in a desperate
OL,8,Fplea for a stranger to donate their
OL,9,Fkidney to her.
OL,11,FThe 65-year-old grandmother said: "I
OL,12,Fdidn't focus on the disease I focused
OL,13,Fon life. There were very few people
OL,14,Fknew about it so I just thought if I
OL,15,Fdon't tell anybody nobody can help me
OL,16,Fso I penned an appeal."
