OL,3,CLong-lost friends brought back
OL,4,Ctogether by life-saving kidney donation
OL,6,FIn a remarkable twist, one person who
OL,7,Fcame forward was no stranger but in
OL,8,Ffact long lost friend Lisa Chapman who
OL,9,FBev had not seen for more than 20
OL,10,Fyears.
OL,12,FTwelve volunteers who replied to the
OL,13,Fpost were tested but mother-of-two
OL,14,FLisa was the best match.
OL,16,FThe 49-year-old said: "I just feel
OL,17,Flike I haven't really done anything so
OL,18,Famazing. She were really good to me
OL,19,Fwhen we knocked about together so it's
OL,20,Fjust lovely that you've helped
OL,21,Fsomebody.
