OL,3,CLong-lost friends brought back
OL,4,Ctogether by life-saving kidney donation
OL,6,F"She's got kids, she's got grandkids
OL,7,Fand giving her that second chance of
OL,8,Flife when she's so active and outgoing
OL,9,Fand such a lovely person it's just
OL,10,Flovely."
OL,12,FBev said she wakes up every morning
OL,13,Fand "just can't believe it."
OL,15,FThey are now raising cash for the
OL,16,FLeeds transplant unit which performed
OL,17,Ftheir surgery - and awareness of
OL,18,Fliving donation.
OL,20,FLisa said the operation has not
OL,21,Fnegatively affected her life at all.
