OL,3,CLong-lost friends brought back
OL,4,Ctogether by life-saving kidney donation
OL,6,FShe said:"I didn't realise you could
OL,7,Factually donate an organ while you
OL,8,Fwere still alive so it's raising that
OL,9,Fawareness that you can save a life and
OL,10,Fstill have a healthy life yourself."
OL,12,FBev said one of the best things to
OL,13,Fcome from the experience is that they
OL,14,Fhave rekindled their friendship.
OL,16,FShe said: "There is a bond. That's one
OL,17,Fof the best things I think. It's a
OL,18,Fbond that a lot of other people don't
OL,19,Fhave."
